{"tid":2077311,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[真送錢] UCLA 10分鐘問卷送你$200","createTime":"2020-06-24T07:46:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T07:46:23.000Z","uid":137255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ccb7b08ed9f4ad9ff62dda3e57d08098ba976fb9","tid":2077311,"uid":137255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:46:23.000Z","msg":"如果你是一位出生於1996/01/01&nbsp;至1998/12/31期間的香港永久居民，你將合資格參與一個由美國加洲大學舉辦的社會問卷調查(約10分鐘長)。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n完成問卷後，你將會有1/ 15的機會獲得一張價值 ~<strong>HK$195 (US$25)&nbsp;的VISA現金禮卡</strong>。共110張電子禮卡將在兩星期被轉發至從1500名受訪者抽出的得獎者之電郵地址。<br />\n<a href=\"https://polisciucla.ca1.qualtrics.com/jfe/form/SV_eIMhAh2xxkRckqp?source=goop\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpolisciucla.ca1.qualtrics.com%2Fjfe%2Fform%2FSV_eIMhAh2xxkRckqp%3Fsource%3Dgoop&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPj2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=4fcd822d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://polisciucla.ca1.qualtrics.com/jfe/form/SV_eIMhAh2xxkRckqp?source=goop</a><br />\n<br />\nUCLA Department of Political Science"}]}